<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> Rescher: فى viener Zeitscher Fur Die Kunde De Morgenlandes, سنة ١٩١٣, ص ٣٧٥ - ٣٩٧.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
